WEBVTT

00:00.403 --> 00:02.322
"Anton has joined the meeting."

00:05.687 --> 00:10.608
While it may be astounding that we can have a virtual meeting  with people on different continents,..

00:12.227 --> 00:14.631
...it can also be frustrating.

00:15.409 --> 00:21.151
And these frustrations can affect morale, engagement, productivity and innovation.

00:22.753 --> 00:28.998
When changes in the ways we communicate lead to changes in how others perceive our communications,...

00:29.192 --> 00:32.462
...this calls for a new set of protocols and behaviors.

